definition: content/calm/still/quiet/safe/secure/in good health/to find a place for/to install/to fix/to fit/to bring (a charge against sb)/to pacify/to harbor (good intentions)/security/safety/peace/ampere
see 安妮·海瑟薇[An1 ni2 · Hai3 se4 wei1]

sentences.english: Anne, too, has come out of her shadow.
sentences.chinese: 安妮也走出了姐姐夏洛蒂和艾米莉的阴影。

sentences.english: Conson your present happy ghost, meet a new girlfriend Annie.
sentences.chinese: 开心鬼的今世康森贵，结识了新女友安妮。

sentences.english: Here Anne had often been staying.
sentences.chinese: 安妮以前经常在这里盘桓。

sentences.english: Betty is going to put up at the Anello Hotel on the third day of her trip to Athens .
sentences.chinese: 贝蒂在她到雅典旅行的第三天，要住宿在安妮罗饭店。

sentences.english: In 1889 Annie Besant was elected to the London School Board .
sentences.chinese: 在1889年安妮贝赞特当选为伦敦学校董事会。

sentences.english: Annie had never married, and was still a fine looking woman at the age of thirty-six.
sentences.chinese: 安妮没结过婚，三十六岁了仍然是个漂亮的女人。

sentences.english: It had petered out soon after Anne's marriage.
sentences.chinese: 其实它早在安妮结婚之后就解散了。

sentences.english: It happened at the well where I was holding a jug while annie pumped.
sentences.chinese: 事情发生在井台旁，我拿著一个水罐，安妮在抽水。

sentences.english: Annie, your husband is a disappointed man.
sentences.chinese: 安妮，你的丈夫是个失意的人。

sentences.english: Harold, Molly or Joanne will help with the job.
sentences.chinese: 哈罗德，莫莉或者乔安妮会协助此工作。

sentences.english: He went to Madame Carp's shop and pretended to help Anneliese.
sentences.chinese: 他到了卡帕女士的商店，假装来帮助安妮丝。

sentences.english: Anne has a flashback about her time in the Espheni Tower.
sentences.chinese: 安妮有一个关于她在艾斯芬尼塔时间倒叙。

sentences.english: In 1866 Annie met the Rev. Frank Besant.
sentences.chinese: 在1866年会见了安妮牧师坦诚贝赞特。

sentences.english: Anne, have you ever seen the movie G-Force?
sentences.chinese: 安妮，你看过豚鼠特工队吗？
